ing: 1 (10 ounce) can diced tomatoes with green chile peppers
des: "This recipe was given to me by a friend. I have since shared it with several people. Serve with cornbread, homemade biscuits, or French bread."
ins: Brown the ground beef in a large skillet over medium heat. Drain any excess fat and add the soup, beans and tomatoes and green chilies. Reduce heat to low, cover and simmer for 15 to 20 minutes.
